2002-08-12  Gediminas Paulauskas <menesis@delfi.lt>

	* Makefile.am: don't build convert.*. fix localedir for Solaris.
	* convert.c, convert.h: remove.
	* runtime-config.c, utf8.c, utils.c: use glib functions for charset
