2001-01-06  Gediminas Paulauskas <menesis@gtranslator.org>

	* pixmaps/untrans.xpm: added this dir and one pixmap for untranslated
		toolbar button.
	* gui.c: use it. Fixed ispell command constructing.
	* header_stuff.c: reformatted *'s
