		Adapted the settings variables to GConf-style.

	* dnd.h: Moved the D'n'D types and enumeration to the
		right places.
	
	* gui.c: The GtkTargetEntries are now settled in here.

	* dnd.h: The enumeration of the D'n'D types is now here.

