	* header_stuff.c & dialogs.c: Use only relative paths as this
		would cause a mess in libgtranslator.

	* \*.c: Merged all gnome_config routines to use the libgtranslator
		routines.

	* prefs.c: Use "Do not..." for "Don't..." in the preferences
		settings.

